serviceDetails: I have been providing high-volume Child Photography services to customers since 2002. Since the, we have captured over a million images on projects ranging from 500 products to 10s of thousands of Child and up to 100,000 images. I wrapped software and operational workflows around the entire Child photography and image production process. We produce images up to 3 times faster than most in-house studios.Image quality and consistency is extremely important to us. With our photography management software, photographers match image views to sample images ensuring consistency. Our 2-step quality control process ensures that images meet your standards. My online portal is accessible 24/7 to all project users. It is easy to see detailed production data including the number of images taken, edited, QAed, formatted and delivered
servicePackage1: All images online in full resolution
